	annote = {Codex collection: AI drug design, protein and peptide {\textbar} EndNote library: 蛋白质分子设计 {\textbar} EndNote ref id: 75 {\textbar} Local PDF path: F:{\textbackslash}Endnote参考文献{\textbackslash}蛋白质分子设计.Data{\textbackslash}PDF{\textbackslash}2474293372{\textbackslash}2025-bioRxiv-Boltzdesign1\_ Inverting All-Atom.pdf {\textbar} Extracted text: F:{\textbackslash}Endnote参考文献{\textbackslash}\_kb{\textbackslash}raw{\textbackslash}extracted\_text{\textbackslash}protein-molecular-design{\textbackslash}ref-75.txt},
