	keywords = {T cell, codex-collection:protein-peptide-design, Codex:AI drug design, protein and peptide, EndNote:蛋白质分子设计, cancer immunotherapy, peptide design, Humans, peptide, immune checkpoint, Immunotherapy/*methods, mirror-image phage display, Neoplasms/*therapy, Peptides/*metabolism, Receptors, Immunologic/*metabolism, Tigit, 分类:蛋白\_多肽设计, import:EndNote全量, 分类:AI药物设计\_蛋白与多肽, EndNote库:蛋白质分子设计, 主题词:T cell {\textbar} peptide design},
