	annote = {Codex collection: AI drug design, protein and peptide {\textbar} EndNote library: 蛋白质分子设计 {\textbar} EndNote ref id: 161 {\textbar} Local PDF path: F:{\textbackslash}Endnote参考文献{\textbackslash}蛋白质分子设计.Data{\textbackslash}PDF{\textbackslash}1918391782{\textbackslash}2026-The Innovation-The evolution of computati.pdf {\textbar} Extracted text: F:{\textbackslash}Endnote参考文献{\textbackslash}\_kb{\textbackslash}raw{\textbackslash}extracted\_text{\textbackslash}protein-molecular-design{\textbackslash}ref-161.txt},
